getJavaName

public String getJavaName()
Returns the name for the parameter used by the java component. If it is the same as a Java-Keyword it will be preceeded by a p_.

Returns:
a String which is the name of the parameter without any conflicts with Java-Keywords

getVariantName

public String getVariantName()
Returns the name for the parameter as it is used by the Variant-variable which is necessary for calls with out-parameters.

Returns:
a String which is the name of the Variant-variable of this parameter
